#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:82
msgid ""
"<strong>Security notice:</strong> The GitHub App private key must never be "
"committed to a repository, shown in browser JavaScript, or saved in a public "
"folder."
msgstr ""

