msgstr ""

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:280
msgid ""
"Deploy & Test reads that JSON and displays the test stats and individual "
"test results in WordPress. Keep the JSON stable and small; use GitHub for "
"full logs and large reports."
msgstr ""

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:311
msgid ""
"The workflow should generate and upload this summary with if: always(), so "
